title: VideoCopilot Element 3D v 1.6.2 (480) - Plugin for AE 64bits Mac
description:
THANKS TO : MrStock , Spider and BiggBirdd

1) Install -> Element3D 162

2) Open After Effects and create a new Composition, then a Solid and apply Element, a pop-up screen will show up. 

3) Click on Generate Request File ( save your request wherever you want ) DON'T CLOSE After Effects.

4) Run "Element 3D Keygen" and Generate a License ( you'll find it on your desktop : "E3D_162.license" )

5) Now go back to After Effects and Load the License you just created.

6) That's it ! ( this License activate also Every 3D Model Pack and Pro-Shaders + Metropolitan + JetStrike )

[b]What if something went wrong ? -> Click "Reset License" and start again from point "2"[/b]

Note : - k/ed plug is 64bit only !
